{"tid":1340994,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"本周文宣重點：元朗暴動，警察失蹤","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T01:59:14.000Z","uid":106482,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"843c7ac3622af256f9cd711493fb6c0aec3be5f4","tid":1340994,"uid":106482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:23:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/645445099/posts/10156981278055100?s=564964925&amp;v=i&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F645445099%2Fposts%2F10156981278055100%3Fs%3D564964925%26v%3Di%26sfns%3Dmo&d=PG0fnU9ECAVDedUX85NM%2FPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=1c379c95\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/645445099/posts/10156981278055100?s=564964925&amp;v=i&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"1642166ce7924dbcd0631c823f011851716846f8","tid":1340994,"uid":70650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb9612071308c5b3823c7f8ac004ba8fa9450711","tid":1340994,"uid":106482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:27:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa0c9436ed5be31410c7f2220855e3a0fd9761ae","tid":1340994,"uid":106482,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:52:19.000Z","msg":"本周文宣重點：元朗暴動，警察失蹤<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓人質事件、928、612、沙田我都有睇live（Sorry冇參與 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ），冇一段比立場女記者被打更令我憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n今日嘅港島遊行未必有好大迴響，搞中聯辦更會令淺藍反感，但係今晚嘅警黑合作絕對係大核彈。小弟建議文宣重點有三：<br />\n<br />\n1. 由我哋主動定義今晚黑社會襲擊市民為暴動。呢班暴徒冇可能承受比義士輕嘅後果。只要我哋同傳媒煲大呢件事做暴動，黑警唔可以唔查，唔可以唔交人，否則只會俾人更差嘅印象。<br />\n<br />\n2. 煲大官警黑合作。現有嘅證據：<br />\na. 何某同黑社會合照, 握手嘅片段 (未 fact check)但老老實實依家流傳張杷唔夠清，唔知有冇其他，或者用TecoGAN試下整清啲？<br />\nb. <a href=\"https://streamable.com/wlfoq（未fact\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fwlfoq%EF%BC%88%E6%9C%AAfact&d=PG0fnU9ECAVDedUX85NM%2FPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=28ec3b47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/wlfoq（未fact</a> check），就咁睇睇唔出右邊係咩人。<br />\nc. 立場live片，明顯見到白衫著草黑警即到，有冇咁巧合？<br />\n一路打緊文，元朗又嚟料... 有更多料靠手足補充<br />\n<br />\n3. 將立場條live片down落嚟，加英文字幕，share去各大外國網。對唔住，要食人血饅頭喇。段片有晒元朗站出事嘅過程，有令人髮指嘅情節：打女記者、打暈女途人、打人老婆、恐嚇婦孺，全部都會觸動左膠神經。之後仲有警察姍姍來遲，同市民對罵，最後用警棍指嚇受害者。條片去外國煲起咗，分分鐘可以幫香港拎返幾個旅遊警告。<br />\n<br />\n以上係小弟愚見。最後請大家唔好唔記得捐錢俾立場！"},{"pid":"8bd912cb9b490fda9179f34370acace0496c50b3","tid":1340994,"uid":106482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:52:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c84c22e1d6aec1c4ad02fcb33555c8b7f260285","tid":1340994,"uid":106482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:54:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"279493392dd24947399e97477816379b33741d2f","tid":1340994,"uid":106482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:59:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3dc83f7da62d23c76eebc71c2c4db353c76edb35","tid":1340994,"uid":221919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:01:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34028de342b1db81856c9cf2917386e4e198896","tid":1340994,"uid":106482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:11:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65877231872891314bbb91723b876b1025ebc2e2","tid":1340994,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:11:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba0df1d6312ec81f74f9d5454f7fb90f539822dc","tid":1340994,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:12:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/27743445015/posts/10157758131430016?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F27743445015%2Fposts%2F10157758131430016%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=PG0fnU9ECAVDedUX85NM%2FPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=b435a51c\" data-auto-